Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

Your hotel reservation for <%= WEDDING[:couple_names_possessive] %> wedding has been confirmed!

Booking Details:
  Confirmation #: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>
  Check-in:   <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
  Check-out:  <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
  Rooms:      <%= @booking.rooms %>
  Nights:     <%= @booking.nights %>
  Total Paid: <%= @booking.amount_display %>
<% if @booking.notes.present? %>
  Notes: <%= @booking.notes %>
<% end %>

If you have any questions about your reservation, please reach out to us directly.

We can't wait to see you there!

<%= WEDDING[:couple_names] %>
